  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-07-28",
    "date": "2022-12-21T15:57:45Z",
    "text": "The LTCH Access and Stability Act\n\nThis bill waives the Medicare site-neutral payment rate for inpatient services at long-term care hospitals for an additional 12 months after the end of the COVID-19 public health emergency. The Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services must report on the effects of this waiver on hospital admissions and overall access to services, among other information."
